high_descs: Turn right and go toward the stove.
Pick up the spoon on the counter to the right of the stove.
Move slightly to the right.
Open the cabinet to the right of the stove.
Put the spoon on the plate in the cabinet and pick it up.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Put the plate with the spoon on it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon on a plate on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right, walk to the counter, turn left.
Pick up the spoon off of the counter.
Take a step to the right.
Put the spoon in the plate under the counter.
Take the plate out of the cabinet.
Turn around, walk to the other side of the room, turn right, walk to the table.
Put the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the spoon on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter at the right of the stove.
Pick up the spoon from the left side of the counter.
Move back from the counter and look at the cabinet underneath.
Open the under-counter cabinet closest to the stove and put the spoon on the plate in the cabinet.
Take the plate with the spoon on it out of the cabinet.
Face left and take the plate and spoon to the far left corner of the room, between the table and wall, then turn to face the end of the table.
Put the stacked spoon and plate on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a spoon on it at the end of the kitchen table.

high_descs: Head to your right and turn left just past the stove so you are facing the kitchen counter
Pick up the spoon from off the kitchen counter
Move slightly to your right and keep facing the counter
Open the kitchen cabinet and place the spoon on the plate
Pick up the plate which has the spoon in it
Turn around, and walk to your right until you reach the trash bag, then turn and face the table
Place the plate with the spoon on it on the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a spoon on it on the kitchen table
